N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 147.3 - Identification of sex offense part-eligible cases

State Regulations

Procedures shall be established in each
court so as to insure that cases pending before it are identified as sex
offense part-eligible at the earliest possible time. Notes
